::: Transanulas ::: Damn it! Can I get a moment of peace!!!!

::: Transanulas walks up to the door, and a blast plate slides over it, 
reinforceing it a little. :::

::: Transanulas then looks to the ceiling, an internal auto-gun drops down 
and targets the door. With a few crossed wires he programs it to fire on 
anything that comes through the door. :::

::: He turns, leaps on Darkmouse, and begins his feast :::
